            "source": [
                "# Boolean Operators\n",
                "\n",
                "Combining logic.\n",
                "\n",
                "## 🎯 Learning Objectives\n",
                "- `and`\n",
                "- `or`\n",
                "- `not`"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "id": "a0f264c7",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "## 1. Keywords, not Symbols\n",
                "\n",
                "Python uses English words, not `&&` or `||`.\n",
                "\n",
                "```python\n",
                "if x > 0 and x < 10:\n",
                "    pass\n",
                "```"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "id": "579c21ef",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "## 2. Negation (`not`)\n",
                "\n",
                "Flips the boolean value.\n",
                "\n",
                "```python\n",
                "print(not True)  # False\n",
                "```"
            ]
        }
    ],
